keys.string: I see Ryn later that night
I could start being preemptively late for tomorrow if you want. But no, I’m done for the day.
You seem a lot more relaxed after class.
I’m basically always asleep. It’s just the teachers care if I fall asleep on them. If I accidentally fall asleep while talk to you, it’s not your fault.
No. I just refuse to drink coffee.
